sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Mercure

    User->>Frontend: Delete a message
    Frontend->>API: DELETE /api/channels/{channelId}/messages/{id}
    API->>API: Validate JWT and author permissions
    API->>DB: Remove message
    DB-->>API: Message deleted
    API->>Mercure: Publish message deletion
    Mercure-->>Frontend: Message removed event
    API-->>Frontend: 204 No Content
    Frontend-->>User: Remove message from thread
